T02TD2393E:22b-1: ti thi ka tsand'a l'i ka n'a ma /
T02TD2393E:22b-3: mu stegs kyi gtum mo zhes bya ba /
T02TD2393E:22b-4: byang chub sems dpa' thal skud can la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2393E:22b-5: bud med gnas ni dbu rgyan m'a //
T02TD2393E:23a-2: srid pa gsum yang sreg par byed //
T02TD2393E:23a-3: me lce nam mkhar khyab par byed //
T02TD2393E:23a-4: aa rtsi na dpal ni gar byed 'gyur //
T02TD2393E:23a-5: nam mkha' rde'u chung sa la rde'u chung brdung //
T02TD2393E:23a-6: rdo rje mi yis rgyu mtsho skems //
T02TD2393E:23a-7: nyi zla gnyis kyang skyabs su gzhug / gar byed dpal gyi aa tsi na thod pa can //
T02TD2393E:23a-8: nam mkhar rde'i chung sa la rde'u chung brdung //
T02TD2393E:23a-9: lha dang lha min mi rnams dang //
T02TD2393E:23a-10: dbang phyug au ma la sogs pa //
T02TD2393E:23a-11: thams cad ye shes me yis bsregs //
T02TD2393E:23a-12: gar byed dpal gyi aa tsa na thod pa can //
T02TD2393E:23a-13: nam mkhar rde'u chung sa la rde'u chung brdung //
T02TD2393E:23a-14: rnal 'byor ma ni khrid byas nas //
T02TD2393E:23a-15: mgon po'i gnas su 'jug par byed //
T02TD2393E:23a-17: gar byed dpal ni aa tsin thod pa can //
T02TD2393E:23a-18: nam mkhar rde'u chung sa rde'u chung brdung //
T02TD2393E:23a-19: mu stegs kyi gtum mo zhes bya ba slob dpon aa tsintas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
